Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is near...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is near!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is etched, and then chaos descends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That dream again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:35.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is etched... and then chaos descends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:13.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Lisanna's grave in the cathedral...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The church said we could \Ndo what we want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now... We're \Nthe ones who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to bring that up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it'd be nice \Nto leave as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:35.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just change the inscription, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought about this at the \Nchurch, but isn't it about time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, paying respect to \Nthe archbishop or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important festival \Nfor the church, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This archbishop person only comes out in \Nfront of people once every few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge number of pilgrims gather just to get \Na glimpse of him, even from far off countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything, do you, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:13.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, at dawn, the Akaza district \Nchurch erupted in a fiery explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been more than 30 cases now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet we still have no \Nclue who is behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've analyzed a number of \Nthe destroyed churches...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Many other countries are watching \Nus carefully at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must discover who is responsible \Nand arrest them in all haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The good name of the Enforcement Corps \Nwill be tarnished at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it will be we, the Magic \NCouncil, that will take the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:38.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make every effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's Memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful... Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a string of church bombings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds quite dangerous to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know him! We met him during \Nthat Nirvana business...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't changed a bit in seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Natsu-nii?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was tired from working in \Nthe fields, so he's taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange that serial bombings \Nlike this just pop up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been out of the loop \Nfor seven years, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:24.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, my prediction powers \Ndon't seem to be working right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see vague, inconclusive things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What smell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-nee, you've got a visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-nee's the one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Lucy Heartfilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's me... And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle Lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making her cry off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:13.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... It's been quite a long time, so \NI suppose it's no surprise you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a tissue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beauty... Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I really don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me start over. I am Michelle Lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long, Lucy-neesan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Neesan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shocking truth! Lucy's old man \Nhad an illegitimate daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:41.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... The Lobster family and the \NHeartfilia family are distantly related.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're Lucy's relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why call her "neesan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's what they mean when \Nthey say "a world of difference"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:54.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but \Nyou're Lucy's daughter, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you draw that conclusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait, why are you addressing \Nme like I'm older?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... You clearly look older than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, are you following \Nwhat they're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like, that Time Ark thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our time stopped for \Nseven years on Tenroujima,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but for everyone else time \Nmoved forward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you consider Lucy's \Nactual age, it's not strange
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:30.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,for Michelle to call her "neesan" \Nas if she's an older relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu seems to be refusing \Nto think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally... I finally am able to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... And by the \Nway, what's that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:45.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to give this... to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for you forever \Nin order to give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop makin' her cry! And \Nyou call yourself a Man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call myself a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this thing is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:11.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we got proof she's related \Nto Lucy... Just as noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:20.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a memento of your \Nfather, Jude Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:27.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped Uncle Jude for a \Nlittle while with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:31.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was there when he passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to pass this along to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:39.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's... last request?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was always worried about \Nyou after you went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:52.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said that he knew you were still alive \Nout there, somewhere, and asked me to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed away peacefully, \Nas if going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:08:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, I've \Nbeen searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I've finally met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I can fulfill \NUncle Jude's dying wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I was told was to give \Nthis case to you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open 'er up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you see what's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:30.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She searched like crazy for you, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let her see this thing \Nshe took all this trouble to deliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This wrapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's got a spell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be what I smelled earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something that Uncle Jude valued?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno... I don't recall \Never seeing it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta be a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it is a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...haven't eaten anything \Nin the past three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:30.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your guild seems like a fun place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My father really is forgetful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he forgot to \Ntell you about Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I found you were \Nin the guild right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. But we'd all disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're a Celestial Wizard, Nee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lucy-chan, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Fairy Tail, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, a lot of them lack any delicacy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:10:00.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're all good folks, and if anything \Nhappens they band together and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And they value their friends above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Jude was really proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to see me, Michelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:27.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! This is my castle now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:32.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to my father that \NI've been able to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait over there, I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not any trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:49.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my mother early, seven years \Nflew by before I realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought I'd have a relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:58.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone in the guild \Nis like my family, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to Iris after this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the tears are about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey, don't read that without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, you write novels?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat or talk: Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find any information on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool. I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:35.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a dream for your future. You're \Nalready a wizard... What a fulfilling life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, are you sure I won't be in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you with open arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:17.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll look for a job here in \NMagnolia and we can share the rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, need a tissue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, if you want work, \Nwhy not work at Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, work at Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle Lobster came to deliver \Na memento to me from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like an older, younger sister \Nthat suddenly showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning, laundry, sewing, cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can do everything, and \Nreally makes my life easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't speak much about herself, \Nbut she seems somehow helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:03.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although there's a lot of things about \Nher you'd mistake at first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something just makes you \Nwant to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to up my game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I wonder if Father got her to \Ncome to me so I wouldn't be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Work! Let's go, Lucy!" ...he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuka-chan, you came today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taken a real liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mustache, mustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to round up some bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:40.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's a wastin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to come see this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I would like to see what \Nit's like being a wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:57.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the part about never knowing \Nwhat'll happen with this team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what will the Master say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:03.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,V-V!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,4th, what say you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no objections, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you get the most out of things that \Nother people say you're not ready for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:22.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how you went off on an S Class \Nquest right after you joined, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Well, why don't you come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be together, and if \Nanything happens, I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:41.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be the "Bandit Hunt in Honor of Lucy\N Getting a Little Sister"! I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:46.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the request flier, the \Nvictims now all suffer from nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like they had a \Nreal number done on 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:52.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers from the kingdom\N scoured the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they all came back\N crying like babies, it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew this sounded dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, is anyone else hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are? I'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:05.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you're more reliable \Nthan the kingdom's soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed it from the client!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your driving is nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, in order to catch the bandits off \Nguard, Lucy and I will ride in the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to provide the illusion \Nof two women traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray, and Michelle who is here to \Nobserve, will hide themselves in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:30.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After they surround us, Lucy will use her \Nsex appeal to distract the ones in front,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the meantime, Natsu and Gray \Nwill clean up the guys in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the rest, we'll attack \Non both sides and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go riding in no carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oho? You have an objection to \Nmy plan? Some nerve you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not budging from this position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't handle transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an odd weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your clothes back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I can handle the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you'll be a decoy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easier if we concentrate our \Nattack power in the back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to be helpful, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a large haul today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, this is the compromise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:24.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to Erza and \Nher annoying plans, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Complain to Erza, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave my side, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go... Erza plan, step one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:41.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well helloooo there, fellas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All set?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this Erza plan, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're like, totally lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step one, success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, how indecent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin is just as shiny as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with Miss Ugly, let's get the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't in the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they've got cosmetic supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, I want sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but {\i1}we're{\i0} the cargo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make a mockery of my plan \NI stayed up all night thinking of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrest you all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:26.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, criminal scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stayed up all night? Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:32.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wizards?! You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not what we expected, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you defile we pure \Nmaidens with your filthy deceit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you look down on us just \Nbecause you were {\i1}born{\i0} a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:50.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what people \Nwere having nightmares of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, Lucy-neesan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Fleuve d'Etoile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, what's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of magic power? That shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you come with \Nus without resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I'm dazzled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your team really is strong, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll try and work hard too next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizards are amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guilds are a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. We make a ton of racket, \Nbut there's never a dull day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what'd you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an acquaintance of \Nmine to look into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki's gone to get the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about making you \Nhandle this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this is what they found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lobster Family really was a wealthy \Nplantation family concentrated in the Zentopia Church Parish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I was worried for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there was the time with \NMest... I mean, Dranbalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:18.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a second. The Lobster family {\i1}was{\i0} a \Nwealthy plantation family? Why the past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:23.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because a number of years \Nago there was a terrible incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:24.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Michelle is a survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Burnt to the ground, and this time corroded?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I consider the distance between each \Nparish, and the varied magic traces,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can come to no other conclusion \Nthan there are multiple culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:43.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have been out \Nwhen the tragedy happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I heard there was \Na body discovered here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was sure this church \Nonly had the one priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who was the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's very insistent that \Nthere was no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Lucy-neesan... I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:15.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you can pay money, guilds \Nwill do what you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, why not request the \Nguild to investigate that memento?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so smart of you, Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of a wizard \Nasking a wizard for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over a request flier upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting in a request for the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something to help you \Nunderstand what Uncle Jude wanted to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then, I'll take it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break it now. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you! I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:05.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's a fateful union?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've both lost their families...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You went and researched \Nher identity... Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am the Master, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I got us \Nthrough these seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something else that's worrying me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's appearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:51.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those ancient letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, get Levy-chan to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:58.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here! She's off far \Naway with Shadow Gear on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so is Fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's trying to tell us something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you read those characters, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy... You'd be better off not \Ngetting involved with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to solve this \Nriddle, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Challenging \NLaxus to a fight, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just never learn, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's not just me! Gajeel's the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you challenge Erza to a \Nfight indiscriminately, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a man \Nalways striving for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a \Nman who doesn't know his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.49,0:24:16.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Raging Battle! Natsu vs. Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's still fighting with that short stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So after becoming an invisible figure, \Nshe wants to be a stick figure?
